<plot>The central character is an old man who commits 3 murders to avenge his business partners' deceit. His murderous trait is underscored by the eccentricity of him singing a bhajan after each one of his murders ("Aayo kuhaan se ghanshaam"). He's also having his eyes peeled for the daughter that he lost track of. Some lilting tunes by Panchamda. His "Naa jaa re", "Raat kali ik khwab", "Bhali bhali si" are remembered to this day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?085497</url></doc>
